{"tid":1489590,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"田北辰引述消息指中央為修例爭議設死線","createTime":"2019-08-20T02:05:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-20T03:33:38.000Z","uid":151248,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"0343354e4afb47dfe73de91bdcb6d09a907e6471","tid":1489590,"uid":151248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T02:05:48.000Z","msg":"實政圓桌立法會議員田北辰在一個電台節目表示，收到消息指中央為本港修例爭議設下死線，要在今年10月1日國慶70周年之前平息風波。<br />\n<br />\n田北辰認為，民陣在本月31日舉行的遊行是平息風波的黃金機會，如果可以令遊行人數大幅減少，並在遊行後不出現暴力事件，就可令中央信服香港局勢平穩。<br />\n<br />\n田北辰又指出，政府成立獨立調查委員會可以平息很多「和理非」市民的怨氣，認為委員會成員要有法律背景、政治中立，以及要極具公信力，否則風波不能平息，中央可能會出動解放軍駐港部隊。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2225083/%E7%94%B0%E5%8C%97%E8%BE%B0%E5%BC%95%E8%BF%B0%E6%B6%88%E6%81%AF%E6%8C%87%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%AE%E7%82%BA%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B%E7%88%AD%E8%AD%B0%E8%A8%AD%E6%AD%BB%E7%B7%9A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F2225083%2F%25E7%2594%25B0%25E5%258C%2597%25E8%25BE%25B0%25E5%25BC%2595%25E8%25BF%25B0%25E6%25B6%2588%25E6%2581%25AF%25E6%258C%2587%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25A4%25AE%25E7%2582%25BA%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E4%25BE%258B%25E7%2588%25AD%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E8%25A8%25AD%25E6%25AD%25BB%25E7%25B7%259A&d=OqNKNX3jJWm7Bjx4wMOex4MY%2BwsNvTr2Nz54cwdIBJg%3D&h=fb772456\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2225083/%E7%94%B0%E5%8C%97%E8%BE%B0%E5%BC%95%E8%BF%B0%E6%B6%88%E6%81%AF%E6%8C%87%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%AE%E7%82%BA%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B%E7%88%AD%E8%AD%B0%E8%A8%AD%E6%AD%BB%E7%B7%9A</a><br />\n<br />\n大家撐住呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85783028b280dfa3581841eec73adc5eb93834e9","tid":1489590,"uid":155137,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T02:11:51.000Z","msg":"搵刀手斬曬啲人咪人數減少"},{"pid":"de2142eb64fa6ac98649f872